Bellotti=E2=80=99s expected departure caused a minor frenzy at the Bally st=
ore on Via Montenapoleone, with editors
from across the globe buying as much of what=E2=80=99s left as they could b=
efore it=E2=80=99s gone. (I visited three times, and secured two pairs of s=
hoes: the hot-red sling backs ( https://www.bally.com/en/products/alva-pump=
