ffer more to persuade them to stay=E2=80=94<em>i.e.</em>, give them more
editorial control, cheaper rates, or both. It=E2=80=99s a dismal state of a=
ffairs.<br/><br/>From what I gathered in Milan, the books with proven luxur=
